-- Mexico's Mexichem says to buy plastic maker Vestolit for $293 mln
-- 
-- Tue Aug 05, 2014 09:38AM EDT
-- None



MEXICO CITY, Aug 5 (Reuters) - Mexico's Mexichem <MEXCHEM.MX> said on Tuesday it had signed a deal to buy Germany-based Vestolit, a maker of durable plastics used for windows floorings and pipes, for 219 million euros ($293.09 million). ($1 = 0.7472 Euros)   (Reporting by Christine Murray)  ((Christine.Murray@thomsonreuters.com; +52-55-5282-7147; Reuters Messaging: christine.murray.thomsonreuters.com@reuters.net))  Keywords: MEXICHEM VESTOLIT/

